{"type": "article", "id": 29629, "title": "灵活调节的灯具", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-14T23:02:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160714181308sM2KIvJf5anY9gC7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>还记得我们曾经介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/29071.html\">平衡灯</a>吗？今天介绍的 Poise 同样是一款鼓励你动手操作的灯具，由来自印度的 <a href=\"http://www.saif-faisal.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Saif Faisal</a> 设计。纤细的灯柱和灯罩均由一整块核桃木片打造，通过一个圆形的金属扣相连，可以自由地沿着灯柱镂空的部分上下移动。金属扣有黄铜和黑色铝合金两种可选，并且和底座材质保持一致。Faisal 为 Poise 设计了台灯和落地灯两种款式，你可以通过 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SAIFFAISAL.designworkshop\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a> 主页与他联系进行订购。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714204153m9nJodK28yU4XCb3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714204153RpGanKx4iuHZ9Ost.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714204153u6nOPaXeGJW1Zjdh.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714204154GWxZAl0HhwoVLuct.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}